{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/post/2025/04-16-AI开发助手-外置知识库思考/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"一席之地","author":"xi ming"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"dff7031b-348a-5366-9e1e-2d34e9a5d2ef","excerpt":"海外机房迁移的事情耽误了好久，中间陆陆续续做了一些尝试，使用Planning-execute 架构的Agent可以将Android Native代码(1500行左右)转MRN…","html":"<p>海外机房迁移的事情耽误了好久，中间陆陆续续做了一些尝试，使用Planning-execute 架构的Agent可以将Android Native代码(1500行左右)转MRN走通了。但是还是有几个问题</p>\n<ol>\n<li>更复杂一些的代码处理就会有一些问题，一次通过率较低</li>\n<li>小规模代码下也存在功能缺失的问题</li>\n<li>部分样式缺失</li>\n<li>在转化的过程中发现MCP起到了负向作用</li>\n</ol>\n<p>1~3 可以通过优化planning来逐步解决，MCP这个还需要分析一下Why。</p>\n<p>1.问题是目前项目中存在大量的组件库，集团的组件库，团队自己封装的通用组件库，业务组件库，框架内自带的，已有的MCP服务给出的信息没有优先级概念</p>\n<p>2.意图识别较差，比如下图</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8333f154488e9a071851eecd291995e5/167b5/image-20250620131953554.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 94.5945945945946%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image-20250620131953554\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/8333f154488e9a071851eecd291995e5/fcda8/image-20250620131953554.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8333f154488e9a071851eecd291995e5/12f09/image-20250620131953554.png 148w,\n/static/8333f154488e9a071851eecd291995e5/e4a3f/image-20250620131953554.png 295w,\n/static/8333f154488e9a071851eecd291995e5/fcda8/image-20250620131953554.png 590w,\n/static/8333f154488e9a071851eecd291995e5/167b5/image-20250620131953554.png 776w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>返回的就完全没什么用</p>","fields":{"slug":"/post/2025/04-16-AI开发助手-外置知识库思考/"},"tableOfContents":"","frontmatter":{"title":"AI开发助手-外置知识库思考","date":"2025年04月16日","description":null,"tags":["思考","AI"]},"wordCount":{"words":27,"paragraphs":10,"sentences":10}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/post/2025/04-16-AI开发助手-外置知识库思考/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/post/2025/04-02-AI开发助手/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"AI开发助手","tags":["思考","AI","Agent"],"description":null}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/post/2025/11-18-UI组件库/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"UI组件库思考","tags":["思考","UI","组件库"],"description":null}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["2887002447","3110208747","3255319198","63159454"],"slicesMap":{}}